    <title>Hexo Fluid 主题配置详解</title>
    <link href="/2024/02/06/hexo-fluid-guide/"/>
    <url>/2024/02/06/hexo-fluid-guide/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Hexo-Fluid-主题配置详解"><a href="#Hexo-Fluid-主题配置详解" class="headerlink" title="Hexo Fluid 主题配置详解"></a>Hexo Fluid 主题配置详解</h1><h2 id="1-顶部导航栏配置"><a href="#1-顶部导航栏配置" class="headerlink" title="1. 顶部导航栏配置"></a>1. 顶部导航栏配置</h2><h3 id="1-1-博客标题"><a href="#1-1-博客标题" class="headerlink" title="1.1 博客标题"></a>1.1 博客标题</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">navbar:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">blog_title:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;我的博客&quot;</span>  <span class="hljs-comment"># 可修改为您想要的博客名称</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-2-毛玻璃效果"><a href="#1-2-毛玻璃效果" class="headerlink" title="1.2 毛玻璃效果"></a>1.2 毛玻璃效果</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">navbar:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">ground_glass:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">enable:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 是否启用</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">blur:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0.7</span>      <span class="hljs-comment"># 模糊度，范围0~1</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-3-导航菜单"><a href="#1-3-导航菜单" class="headerlink" title="1.3 导航菜单"></a>1.3 导航菜单</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">navbar:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">menu:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> &#123; <span class="hljs-attr">key:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;首页&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">link:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;/&quot;</span> &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> &#123; <span class="hljs-attr">key:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;归档&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">link:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;/archives/&quot;</span> &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> &#123; <span class="hljs-attr">key:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;分类&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">link:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;/categories/&quot;</span> &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> &#123; <span class="hljs-attr">key:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;标签&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">link:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;/tags/&quot;</span> &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> &#123; <span class="hljs-attr">key:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;关于&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">link:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;/about/&quot;</span> &#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>您可以：</p><ul><li>修改菜单项的显示文字（key）</li><li>添加新的菜单项</li><li>修改链接地址（link）</li></ul><h2 id="2-首页横幅配置"><a href="#2-首页横幅配置" class="headerlink" title="2. 首页横幅配置"></a>2. 首页横幅配置</h2><h3 id="2-1-横幅图片"><a href="#2-1-横幅图片" class="headerlink" title="2.1 横幅图片"></a>2.1 横幅图片</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">index:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">banner_img:</span> <span class="hljs-string">/images/banner.jpg</span>  <span class="hljs-comment"># 图片路径</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>需要您：</p><ol><li>准备一张高质量的横幅图片（建议尺寸：1920x1080px）</li><li>将图片放在 <code>source/images/</code> 目录下</li><li>修改配置中的图片路径</li></ol><h3 id="2-2-横幅高度与遮罩"><a href="#2-2-横幅高度与遮罩" class="headerlink" title="2.2 横幅高度与遮罩"></a>2.2 横幅高度与遮罩</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">index:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">banner_img_height:</span> <span class="hljs-number">85</span>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 高度（建议范围：60~100）</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">banner_mask_alpha:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0.3</span>   <span class="hljs-comment"># 遮罩透明度（0~1）</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-3-首页标语"><a href="#2-3-首页标语" class="headerlink" title="2.3 首页标语"></a>2.3 首页标语</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">index:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">slogan:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">enable:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">text:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;分享技术，记录生活&quot;</span>   <span class="hljs-comment"># 您的口号</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">font_size:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1.</span><span class="hljs-string">5rem</span>           <span class="hljs-comment"># 字体大小</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">line_height:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1.5</span>           <span class="hljs-comment"># 行高</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3-文章卡片设置"><a href="#3-文章卡片设置" class="headerlink" title="3. 文章卡片设置"></a>3. 文章卡片设置</h2><h3 id="3-1-文章信息显示"><a href="#3-1-文章信息显示" class="headerlink" title="3.1 文章信息显示"></a>3.1 文章信息显示</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">index:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">post_meta:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">date:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>      <span class="hljs-comment"># 显示日期</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">category:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>  <span class="hljs-comment"># 显示分类</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">tag:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>      <span class="hljs-comment"># 显示标签</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-2-文章摘要"><a href="#3-2-文章摘要" class="headerlink" title="3.2 文章摘要"></a>3.2 文章摘要</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">index:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">article_img_align:</span> <span class="hljs-string">left</span>   <span class="hljs-comment"># 图片位置：left/right/center</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">excerpt_type:</span> <span class="hljs-string">text</span>       <span class="hljs-comment"># 摘要类型：text/html</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">excerpt_length:</span> <span class="hljs-number">200</span>      <span class="hljs-comment"># 摘要长度</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">auto_excerpt:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">enable:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>          <span class="hljs-comment"># 自动摘要</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4-颜色主题"><a href="#4-颜色主题" class="headerlink" title="4. 颜色主题"></a>4. 颜色主题</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">color:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">body_bg_color:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;#f8f9fa&quot;</span>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 背景色</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">board_color:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;#fff&quot;</span>             <span class="hljs-comment"># 板块背景色</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">text_color:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;#3c4858&quot;</span>          <span class="hljs-comment"># 文字颜色</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">link_color:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;#3c4858&quot;</span>          <span class="hljs-comment"># 链接颜色</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">link_hover_color:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;#1abc9c&quot;</span>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 链接悬停颜色</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="5-需要创建的页面"><a href="#5-需要创建的页面" class="headerlink" title="5. 需要创建的页面"></a>5. 需要创建的页面</h2><p>要使所有功能正常工作，您需要创建以下页面：</p><ol><li><p>分类页：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo new page categories<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>标签页：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo new page tags<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>关于页：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo new page about<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="6-自定义修改步骤"><a href="#6-自定义修改步骤" class="headerlink" title="6. 自定义修改步骤"></a>6. 自定义修改步骤</h2><ol><li><p>修改导航栏</p><ul><li>编辑 <code>_config.fluid.yml</code> 中的 <code>navbar</code> 部分</li><li>设置您的博客标题</li><li>调整毛玻璃效果</li></ul></li><li><p>配置首页横幅</p><ul><li>准备并添加横幅图片</li><li>调整横幅高度和遮罩透明度</li><li>设置个性化的首页标语</li></ul></li><li><p>调整文章显示</p><ul><li>配置文章信息的显示项</li><li>设置文章摘要的显示方式</li><li>调整图片对齐方式</li></ul></li><li><p>个性化配色</p><ul><li>修改背景色</li><li>调整文字和链接颜色</li><li>设置悬停效果</li></ul></li></ol><p>我们可以一起逐步调整这些设置，打造一个独特的博客风格。您想先从哪个部分开始修改？ </p>]]></content>
    
    
